.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: turquise, ebony, azure, pink, apricot
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, australian, malaysian, mexican, pakistani
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-lemonade, 7up, lemonade, cola, almond-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: turquisemaster, bongani, fonseca, swisher, montecristo
5 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, pony, goldfish, rabbit
1. the japanese is the person who likes azure
2. the swedish is the owner of the pony
3. the australian is the person drinking cola
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes pink
5. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking 7up
6. the fonseca-smoker is the owner of the goat
7. the person who likes apricot is the bongani-smoker
8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle
9. the mexican is on the far left
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster
11. the owner of the rabbits is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker
12. the turquisemaster-smoker is the person drinking soy-lemonade
13. the malaysian is the swisher-smoker
14. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise
15. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    apricot	|     turquise	|      azure	|     ebony	|     pink	|
| Nationality	|   mexican	|    australian	|    japanese	|    malaysian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     hamster	|    rabbit	|     goat	|     goldfish	|      pony	|
| Beverage	|    almond-milk	|     cola	|     lemonade	|    7up	|      soy-lemonade	|
| Cigar		|   bongani	|    montecristo	|  fonseca	|    swisher	|   turquisemaster	|
